44
00:02:46.520 --> 00:02:51.400
Mu-Mutta Don...
Jos palaamme Grand Linelle,

45
00:02:51.400 --> 00:02:55.660
emmekΟΕ vain tΟΕrmΟΛisi taas johonkin
HaukansilmΟΛ-Mihawkin kaltaiseen?

46
00:02:59.530 --> 00:03:03.660
