139
00:09:42.190 --> 00:09:43.810
KΟΛydΟΛΟΛn pΟΛΟΛlle!

140
00:09:51.950 --> 00:09:54.370
Aseita tai ei, kokki on kokki

141
00:09:54.370 --> 00:09:57.740
Me taas taistelemme tyΟΕksemme.

142
00:09:57.740 --> 00:10:02.370
